detected_clauses.detection_method: Identified roles of Landlord and Tenant, and reference to Premises and Project.
detected_clauses.supporting_text: Landlord, as the Landlord, rents to Tenant, as the Tenant, the Premises referred to as ... which is part of the Project known as ...
detected_clauses.summary: Identifies parties involved and the property being leased.

detected_clauses.detection_method: Found keywords indicating rental agreement commencement and termination conditions.
detected_clauses.supporting_text: The rental agreement will commence [DATE] and continue on a month-to-month basis. Either party, on 30-days’ written notice, may terminate this rental agreement.
detected_clauses.summary: Rental agreement starts on [DATE] and is month-to-month with a 30-day termination notice.

detected_clauses.detection_method: Identified currency amounts and payment terms.
detected_clauses.supporting_text: Tenant to pay, in advance, $5,000 monthly rent on the first day of each month... Tenant to pay a charge of $[AMOUNT] or [PERCENT]% of the delinquent rent payment...
detected_clauses.summary: Monthly rent of $5,000 due on the 1st, with a late fee structure.

detected_clauses.detection_method: Identified conditions regarding possession delivery and tenant's rights.

extracted_data.possession_delivery: on commencement of the rental agreement
extracted_data.tenant_rights: terminate if possession not delivered within 10 days

detected_clauses.supporting_text: Possession to be delivered to Tenant on commencement of the rental agreement... Tenant may terminate the rental agreement if Landlord does not deliver possession within 10 days.
detected_clauses.summary: Possession is to be delivered at the start of the lease, with tenant rights to terminate if delayed.

detected_clauses.detection_method: Identified responsibilities for maintenance and repair.

extracted_data.tenant_responsibility: keep the Premises in good order and repair

detected_clauses.supporting_text: Tenant will keep the Premises and its improvements in good order... Landlord will maintain in good order, condition and repair the structures and common area components...
detected_clauses.summary: Tenant is responsible for maintaining the Premises, while the Landlord maintains common areas.

detected_clauses.supporting_text: Tenant will obtain and maintain commercial general liability... Tenant will obtain and maintain a standard fire insurance policy...
detected_clauses.summary: Tenant must maintain liability and fire insurance at specified coverage levels.

detected_clauses.detection_method: Identified permitted uses and restrictions on the Premises.
detected_clauses.supporting_text: The Tenant’s use of the Premises will be [USE]. No other use of the Premises is permitted.
detected_clauses.summary: Tenant's use of the Premises is restricted to specified purposes.

detected_clauses.summary: Landlord has rights to collect losses if Tenant breaches the agreement.
